data.description: Wow! Move In Ready! A Modern Beautiful End Unit Townhome located in the sought after gated community of Osprey Lakes. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, and a 1 car garage (with a two-car driveway). This two-story, all concrete block constructed home offers a spacious, open concept with over 1700 sq. ft. of living area with plenty of space to entertain family and friends. As you walk into the home you will see the wide and welcoming entryway that leads into the main floor which boasts a beautiful kitchen with plenty of cabinets. The grand island is perfect to gather around to have breakfast or entertain. The dining area is large enough for a full size table and there's a wonderful spacious great room. Three large glass sliding doors lead out to an enclosed screened in lanai. The second Floor Master bedroom has two walk-in closets in the bathroom with double vanity sinks. There's a Open Bonus Room that can be use for an office. Also located on the second floor are two additional large bedrooms and a full-size Jack and Jill bathroom. The laundry area is also conveniently located on the second floor. This home is equipped with hurricane shutters and Osprey Lakes has NO CDD fees and low HOA fees which cover water, landscaping, exterior maintenance, and the gate. The Osprey Lakes community features a small lake in the center and dog walk area. Exceptionally convenient location in the heart of Riverview and close to all major Highways and the Leroy Selmon Cross Town while also being close to downtown Tampa and still within a short drive to restaurants and shopping. This is a must see home that won't last long!
